FBIS4-60501 "drnes102bb_94001" FBIS-NES-94-102 Daily Report 24 May 1994 Inter-Arab Affairs Libya Seeks AMU Action To End Yemen Conflict Libya Seeks AMU Action To End Yemen Conflict LD2405135994 Tripoli Great Jamahiriyah Radio Network in Arabic 1230 GMT 24 May 94 LD2405135994 Tripoli Great Jamahiriyah Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] The brother secretary of the General People's Committee for Unity has sent a message to the brother minister of foreign affairs in Algeria in his capacity as chairman of the Arab Maghreb Union [AMU] foreign ministers' council. The message stresses the need for the AMU to take united action toward the current developments in Yemen, to work toward ending the fighting between the brothers, and to preserve the territorial integrity of Yemen in accordance with the treaty of the Arab Maghreb unity and in implementation of the resolutions of the Union's presidential council.
